---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for the Ocean Recoveries Lab website."
>
  <section class="section bg-surface">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-lg">
        <p class="lead">
          The Ocean Recoveries Lab at UC Santa Barbara is committed to protecting your privacy.
          This policy explains how we handle information collected through this website.
        </p>

        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>
          This website does not collect personal information unless you voluntarily provide it
          (for example, by emailing us directly). We do not use cookies for tracking purposes.
        </p>

        <h2>Analytics</h2>
        <p>
          We may use privacy-respecting analytics to understand how visitors use our site.
          This data is aggregated and does not identify individual visitors.
        </p>

        <h2>External Links</h2>
        <p>
          This site contains links to external websites (Google Scholar, GitHub, ORCID, etc.).
          We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these external sites.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact Information</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at
          <a href="mailto:astier@ucsb.edu">astier@ucsb.edu</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>UC Santa Barbara Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          As part of the University of California system, this website is also subject to the
          <a href="https://www.policy.ucsb.edu/policies/all-policies/information-technology/information-privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            UC Santa Barbara privacy policies
          </a>.
        </p>

        <p class="text-sm text-muted mt-8">
          Last updated: December 2024
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose h2 {
    @apply text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4;
  }

  .prose p {
    @apply text-muted mb-4 leading-relaxed;
  }

  .prose a {
    @apply text-accent hover:underline;
  }
</style>
